    <title>HTML基础语法</title>
    <url>/2022-02-11/16-24-09/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="HTML基础语法"><a href="#HTML基础语法" class="headerlink" title="HTML基础语法"></a>HTML基础语法</h1><p><a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/html/index.asp">W3Cschool的HTML基础教程</a></p>
<h2 id="一、基本框架"><a href="#一、基本框架" class="headerlink" title="一、基本框架"></a>一、基本框架</h2><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">        <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span>网页标签名<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">title</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    网页主体</span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<hr>
<h2 id="二、主体样式"><a href="#二、主体样式" class="headerlink" title="二、主体样式"></a>二、主体样式</h2><ul>
<li><h3 id="标题大小"><a href="#标题大小" class="headerlink" title="标题大小"></a>标题大小</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span>一级标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h1</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span>二级标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h2</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h3</span>&gt;</span>三级标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h3</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h4</span>&gt;</span>四级标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h4</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h5</span>&gt;</span>五级标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h5</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">h6</span>&gt;</span>六级标题<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">h6</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<h1>一级标题</h1>
<h2>二级标题</h2>
<h3>三级标题</h3>
<h4>四级标题</h4>
<h5>五级标题</h5>
<h6>六级标题</h6></blockquote>
</li>
<li><h3 id="字体样式"><a href="#字体样式" class="headerlink" title="字体样式"></a>字体样式</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">font</span> <span class="attr">face</span>=<span class="string">&quot;华文新魏&quot;</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">&quot;5&quot;</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">&quot;#ffc0cb&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--更改文本字体大小颜色（color可用单词或者&quot;rgb(值1,值2,值3)&quot;）&lt;/font&gt;--&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p><font face="华文新魏" size="5" color="#ffc0cb">更改文本字体大小颜色（color可用单词或者”rgb(值1,值2,值3)”）</font></p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><h3 id="粗体"><a href="#粗体" class="headerlink" title="粗体"></a>粗体</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span>粗体<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">b</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p><b>粗体</b></p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><h3 id="斜体"><a href="#斜体" class="headerlink" title="斜体"></a>斜体</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span>斜体<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">i</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p><i>斜体</i></p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><h3 id="下划线"><a href="#下划线" class="headerlink" title="下划线"></a>下划线</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span>下划线<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">u</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p><u>下划线</u></p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><h3 id="文本居中"><a href="#文本居中" class="headerlink" title="文本居中"></a>文本居中</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span>文本居中<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">center</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<center>文本居中</center></blockquote>
</li>
<li><h3 id="段落标签"><a href="#段落标签" class="headerlink" title="段落标签"></a>段落标签</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>段落标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span>段落标签<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">p</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>段落标签</p><p>段落标签</p></blockquote>
</li>
<li><h3 id="文本换行"><a href="#文本换行" class="headerlink" title="文本换行"></a>文本换行</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">文本换行<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span>文本换行</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>文本换行<br>文本换行</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><h3 id="分割线"><a href="#分割线" class="headerlink" title="分割线"></a>分割线</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">or</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">hr</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;hr_t&quot;</span> <span class="attr">size</span>=<span class="string">10</span> <span class="attr">color</span>=<span class="string">&quot;red&quot;</span> <span class="attr">style</span>=<span class="string">&quot;border:1 solid  #999&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<hr class="hr_t" size=10 color="red" style="border:1 solid  #999" /></blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="三、转义字符"><a href="#三、转义字符" class="headerlink" title="三、转义字符"></a>三、转义字符</h2><p><a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/html/html_entities.asp">HTML 字符实体</a></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">                   实体名称                实体编号</span><br><span class="line">空格                <span class="symbol">&amp;nbsp;</span>                 <span class="symbol">&amp;#160;</span></span><br><span class="line">小于号              <span class="symbol">&amp;lt;</span>                   <span class="symbol">&amp;#60;</span></span><br><span class="line">大于号              <span class="symbol">&amp;gt;</span>                   <span class="symbol">&amp;#62;</span></span><br><span class="line">和号                <span class="symbol">&amp;amp;</span>                  <span class="symbol">&amp;#38;</span></span><br><span class="line">引号                <span class="symbol">&amp;quot;</span>                 <span class="symbol">&amp;#34;</span></span><br><span class="line">撇号                <span class="symbol">&amp;apos;</span>(IE不支持)       <span class="symbol">&amp;#39;</span></span><br><span class="line">小节                <span class="symbol">&amp;sect;</span>                 <span class="symbol">&amp;#167;</span></span><br><span class="line">版权(copyright)     <span class="symbol">&amp;copy;</span>                 <span class="symbol">&amp;#169;</span></span><br><span class="line">注册商标            <span class="symbol">&amp;reg;</span>                  <span class="symbol">&amp;#174;</span></span><br><span class="line">商标                <span class="symbol">&amp;trade;</span>                <span class="symbol">&amp;#8482;</span></span><br><span class="line">乘号                <span class="symbol">&amp;times;</span>                <span class="symbol">&amp;#215;</span></span><br><span class="line">除号                <span class="symbol">&amp;divide;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<blockquote>
<p>空格    《&nbsp;    &#160;》</p>
<p>小于号    《&lt;    &#60;》</p>
<p>大于号    《&gt;    &#62;》</p>
<p>和号    《&amp;    &#38;》</p>
<p>引号    《&quot;    &#34;》</p>
<p>撇号     《&apos;  &#39;》</p>
<p>小节    《&sect;    &#167;》</p>
<p>版权（copyright）    《&copy;    &#169;》</p>
<p>注册商标    《&reg;    &#174;》</p>
<p>商标    《&trade;    &#8482;》</p>
<p>乘号    《&times;    &#215;》</p>
<p>除号    《&divide;》</p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="四、媒体标签"><a href="#四、媒体标签" class="headerlink" title="四、媒体标签"></a>四、媒体标签</h2><ul>
<li><h3 id="图片"><a href="#图片" class="headerlink" title="图片"></a>图片</h3><p><a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/html/html_images.asp">HTML 图像</a></p>
<blockquote>
<p>高度、宽度默认为px像素，加百分号width=”宽度%” height=”高度%”指占&lt;body&gt;的百分比</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;url&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;宽度&quot;</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">&quot;高度&quot;</span>/&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>给图片加属性（鼠标移上去显示的注释）</p>
</blockquote>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">img</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;url&quot;</span> <span class="attr">alt</span>=<span class="string">&quot;写注释&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li>
<li><h3 id="音频"><a href="#音频" class="headerlink" title="音频"></a>音频</h3><p><a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/html/html_audio.asp">HTML 音频</a></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">audio</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;song.mp3&quot;</span> <span class="attr">controls</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">audio</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--controls显示播放控件--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">or</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">audio</span> <span class="attr">controls</span>=<span class="string">&quot;controls&quot;</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">&quot;100&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;100&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">source</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;song.mp3&quot;</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;audio/mp3&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">source</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;song.ogg&quot;</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;audio/ogg&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">embed</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">&quot;100&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;100&quot;</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;song.mp3&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">audio</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>上面的例子使用了两个不同的音频格式<br>HTML5&lt;audio&gt;元素会尝试以 mp3、wmv 或 ogg 来播放音频。如果失败，代码将回退尝试&lt;embed&gt;元素</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
<li><h3 id="视频"><a href="#视频" class="headerlink" title="视频"></a>视频</h3><p><a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/html/html_video.asp">HTML 视频</a></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">video</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;video.mp4&quot;</span> <span class="attr">controls</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">video</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--controls显示播放控件--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">or</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">video</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;320&quot;</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">&quot;240&quot;</span> <span class="attr">controls</span>=<span class="string">&quot;controls&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">source</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;movie.mp4&quot;</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;video/mp4&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">source</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;movie.ogg&quot;</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;video/ogg&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">source</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;movie.webm&quot;</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;video/webm&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">object</span> <span class="attr">data</span>=<span class="string">&quot;movie.mp4&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;320&quot;</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">&quot;240&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">embed</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">&quot;movie.swf&quot;</span> <span class="attr">width</span>=<span class="string">&quot;320&quot;</span> <span class="attr">height</span>=<span class="string">&quot;240&quot;</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">object</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">video</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>上例中使用了 4 中不同的视频格式<br>HTML5&lt;video&gt;元素会尝试播放以 mp4、ogg 或 webm 格式中的一种来播放视频。如果失败，则回退到&lt;embed&gt;元素</p>
</blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="五、超链接标签"><a href="#五、超链接标签" class="headerlink" title="五、超链接标签"></a>五、超链接标签</h2><p><a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/html/html_links.asp">HTML 链接</a></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">a</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">&quot;url&quot;</span> <span class="attr">target</span>=<span class="string">&quot;模式&quot;</span>&gt;</span>链接名称<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">a</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--模式为“_self”就是在当前页面打开，&quot;_blank&quot;就是新页面打开--&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p><a href="链接地址">链接名称</a></p>
</blockquote>
<h2 id="六、列表标签"><a href="#六、列表标签" class="headerlink" title="六、列表标签"></a>六、列表标签</h2><p><a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/html/html_lists.asp">HTML 列表</a></p>
<ul>
<li><h3 id="有序号的列表"><a href="#有序号的列表" class="headerlink" title="有序号的列表"></a>有序号的列表</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>Coffee<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>Milk<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--列表项内部可以使用段落、换行符、图片、链接以及其他列表等等--&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<ol>
<li>Coffee</li>
<li>Milk</li>
</ol></blockquote>
</li>
<li><h3 id="无序号的列表"><a href="#无序号的列表" class="headerlink" title="无序号的列表"></a>无序号的列表</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>Coffee<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span>Milk<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">li</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">ol</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--列表项内部可以使用段落、换行符、图片、链接以及其他列表等等--&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<ul>
<li>Coffee</li>
<li>Milk</li>
</ul></blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
<hr>
<h2 id="七、表格标签"><a href="#七、表格标签" class="headerlink" title="七、表格标签"></a>七、表格标签</h2><p><a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/html/html_tables.asp">HTML 表格</a></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">table</span> <span class="attr">width</span> = <span class="string">&quot;200&quot;</span> <span class="attr">border</span>=<span class="string">&quot;1&quot;</span> <span class="attr">cellspacing</span>=<span class="string">&quot;23&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!--加border表示边框，0为无边框，width为表格宽度，cellspacing为格子的空白大小--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!--tr包起来为一行--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span> <span class="attr">colspan</span> = <span class="string">&quot;2&quot;</span>&gt;</span>Heading<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!--表头--&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!--colspan = &quot;2&quot;表示横跨2列--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span>Another Heading<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">th</span>&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!--另一个表头--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span> <span class="attr">align</span>=<span class="string">&quot;center&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!--align定义对齐方式--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span> <span class="attr">rowspan</span>=<span class="string">&quot;2&quot;</span>&gt;</span>row 1, cell 1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!--rowspan = &quot;2&quot;表示竖跨2行--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>row 1, cell 2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>row 2, cell 1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span>row 2, cell 2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">td</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">tr</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">table</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<table width = "2200" border="1" cellspacing="23">
<tr align="center">
<th colspan = "2">Heading</th>
<th>Another Heading</th>
