<h2 id="八、表单标签"><a href="#八、表单标签" class="headerlink" title="八、表单标签"></a>八、表单标签</h2><p><a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/html/html_forms.asp">HTML 表单</a></p>
<ul>
<li><h3 id="lt-input-gt-元素通过type控制形式"><a href="#lt-input-gt-元素通过type控制形式" class="headerlink" title="&lt;input&gt;元素通过type控制形式"></a>&lt;input&gt;元素通过type控制形式</h3><p><a href="https://www.w3school.com.cn/html/html_form_input_types.asp">&lt;input&gt;包含的type输入类型</a></p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment">&lt;!--action表示提交时的动作，如果省略，会被设置为当前页面；</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="comment">method用get，请求参数会在url后面，长度限制4kb；用post参数会在http协议的请求体中，无限制--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">form</span> <span class="attr">action</span>=<span class="string">&quot;#&quot;</span> <span class="attr">method</span>=<span class="string">&quot;get&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">label</span> <span class="attr">for</span>=<span class="string">&quot;wenzi&quot;</span>&gt;</span>文字:<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">label</span>&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!--下面的input设置一个id，将文字用label包起来指向id，可以在单击文字时直接选择input项（每个type元素都行）--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;text&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;getaName&quot;</span> <span class="attr">id</span>=<span class="string">&quot;wenzi&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!--type表示输入类型，name会作为提交后数值的键值key--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">按钮:<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;submit&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">选项:<span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;radio&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;sameName&quot;</span> <span class="attr">checked</span>&gt;</span>选项1<span class="comment">&lt;!--要设置单选只要传递同一个参数name就可以了--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">br</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">input</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">&quot;radio&quot;</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;sameName&quot;</span>&gt;</span>选项2</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">form</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<form action="#" method="get">
<label for="wenzi">文字:</label>
<br>
<input type="text" name="getaName" id="wenzi">
<br>
按钮:<br>
<input type="submit">
<br>
选项:<br>
<input type="radio" name="sameName" value="1">选项1<!--value的值为提交后的值，与name的键值key对应-->
<br>
<input type="radio" name="sameName" value="2">选项2
</form> </blockquote>
</li>
<li><h3 id="lt-select-gt-下拉列表-lt-option-gt-定义列表项"><a href="#lt-select-gt-下拉列表-lt-option-gt-定义列表项" class="headerlink" title="&lt;select&gt;下拉列表&lt;option&gt;定义列表项"></a>&lt;select&gt;下拉列表&lt;option&gt;定义列表项</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">请选择 <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">select</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;options&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;option1&quot;</span>&gt;</span>选项1<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;option2&quot;</span>&gt;</span>选项2<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;option3&quot;</span>&gt;</span>选项3<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">option</span> <span class="attr">value</span>=<span class="string">&quot;option4&quot;</span>&gt;</span>选项4<span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">option</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">select</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>请选择 <select name="options"></p>
<option value="option1">选项1</option>
<option>选项2</option><!--不加value就会提交包起来的数据-->
<option value="option3">选项3</option>
<option value="option4">选项4</option>
</select></blockquote>
</li>
<li><h3 id="lt-textarea-gt-文本框"><a href="#lt-textarea-gt-文本框" class="headerlink" title="&lt;textarea&gt;文本框"></a>&lt;textarea&gt;文本框</h3><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">请输入文字</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">textarea</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">&quot;message&quot;</span> <span class="attr">rows</span>=<span class="string">&quot;5&quot;</span> <span class="attr">cols</span>=<span class="string">&quot;30&quot;</span>&gt;</span><span class="comment">&lt;!--rows是设定行高尺寸，cols是设定字数宽度尺寸--&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">The cat was playing in the garden.</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">textarea</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<blockquote>
<p>请输入文字</p>
<textarea name="message" rows="5" cols="30">
默认显示文本。
</textarea></blockquote>
</li>
</ul>
